Package: poptrend
Title: Estimate Smooth Trends from Population Count Survey Data
Version: 0.1
Maintainer: Jonas Knape  <jonas.knape@slu.se>
Author: Jonas Knape
Description: Functions to estimate and plot smooth population trends from animal or plant count survey data.
